<div class="title">Horny Like Hell on this Combination</div>
<div class="substance">MDMA & 2C-B</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Oldman&Exact=1">Oldman</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Oldman. "Horny Like Hell on this Combination: An Experience with MDMA & 2C-B (exp5758)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Mar 20, 2001. erowid.org/exp/5758</div>

<br/>



